<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>MobiControl Tools</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrap">

<header class="top">
<div>
<h1>MobiControl Tools</h1>
<div class="sub">Choose a tool to get started.</div>
</div>
<div style="display:flex;gap:16px;align-items:center;">
<span class="signed-in">Signed in as <%= username %></span>
<a href="/logout" class="back">Sign out</a>
</div>
</header>

<div class="menucards">
<a class="menucard" href="/dashboard">
<div class="menucard-icon">&#128202;</div>
<h2>Telecom Data Usage</h2>
<p>Upload a MobiControl Telecom Data Usage report and explore consumption by application, device, and group.</p>
<span class="back">Open &rarr;</span>
</a>

<a class="menucard" href="/device-status">
<div class="menucard-icon">&#128241;</div>
<h2>AIS Data Usage Report Analysis</h2>
<p>Live device status from MobiControl (battery, connection, cellular) joined with AIS-carrier usage from an uploaded report.</p>
<span class="back">Open &rarr;</span>
</a>
</div>

</div>
</body>
</html>
